3rd Edit: 16 lbs down!
4th Edit: Hit a bit of a plateau for a couple of weeks, but I'm starting to lose a bit of weight again. 17.2 lbs down! 😁
5th Edit: 20 lbs down! :D It's hard work, but I'm going slow and steady. I started 12 - hr night shifts, so it's been hard to balance work and self-care.
6th Edit: 22 lbs down! :) I find that it's a bit harder to lose weight, not sure if I'm losing fat and gaining muscle. Hit a bit of a plateau, but I'm going to keep going and try eating healthier.
7th Edit: 12 lbs down! It's been a minute since I posted. Lots of ups and downs and stress over the past couple of months, but still determined to get healthy.
